article.headline: TCU 81, Florida State 68
article.story:
MALIBU, Calif. (AP) -- Sandora Irvin had 14 points and seven
rebounds, and No. 22 TCU beat Florida State 81-68 in the Malibu
Beach Classic on Saturday night.

Ebony Shaw and Adrianne Ross added 13 points apiece for the
Horned Frogs (7-1), and Ashley Davis scored 12 points on 6-of-8
shooting.

Lauren Bradley had 15 points and seven rebounds for Florida
State (5-3). Angela Sutton added 14 points.

TCU (7-1) shot 41.7 percent in the first half on the way to a
37-30 lead. The Horned Frogs pulled away in the second half, making
13 of 27 shots including four of nine 3-pointers.

Natasha Lacy had eight assists for TCU.
